ing-news/elden-ring-patch-should-make-it-easier-for-shadow-of-the-erdtree-players-3769118"><em>《Elden Ring》</em>补丁刚刚发布，这使得游戏变得更加容易</a>。也许如果它在凯演奏时出现，他会更快地击败它。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/streamer-dies-1070-times-trying-to-beat-elden-ring-shadow-of-the-erdtree-3769177">主播在试图击败《Elden Ring: Shadow Of The Erdtree》时死了 1070 次，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
